2 HOUSE BILL 191
1 Article – Commercial Law
2 Section 13–301(14)(xlvii)
3 Annotated Code of Maryland
4 (2025 Replacement Volume)
5 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
6 Article – Commercial Law
7 Section 13–301(14)(xlviii)
8 Annotated Code of Maryland
9 (2025 Replacement Volume)
10 BY adding to
11 Article – Commercial Law
12 Section 13–301(14)(xlix) and 14–1330
